# Generative UI — "Generate from prompt" (local-only, subscription-powered).
#
# Generation runs on YOUR Claude subscription via the Claude Code CLI — there is
# no metered API key and no per-token billing. It only works where the `claude`
# binary is installed and logged in (your machine); the deployed site stays the
# pure JSON sandbox with the Generate action hidden.
#
# Setup (once):
#   1. Install Claude Code:  https://docs.claude.com/claude-code
#   2. Generate a token:     claude setup-token
#   3. Paste it below, then restart `npm run dev`.
# (If you're already logged into Claude Code on this machine, the CLI's stored
#  login is used and this can be left blank.)
CLAUDE_CODE_OAUTH_TOKEN=

# Optional: model used for generation (defaults to the Claude Code CLI default).
# SANDY_GENERATE_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8
